We shouldn't have followed them.

282
00:22:31,230 --> 00:22:33,110
That's right.
It's their honeymoon.

283
00:22:33,110 --> 00:22:36,040
<i>Do you want to have a wedding
and go on a honeymoon too?</i>

284
00:22:36,570 --> 00:22:39,270
They must be crazy.

285
00:22:39,270 --> 00:22:42,190
