295
00:23:19,130 --> 00:23:20,130
It's mine.

296
00:23:22,370 --> 00:23:23,250
Hello?

297
00:23:23,250 --> 00:23:24,300
Yes.

298
00:23:24,840 --> 00:23:26,480
