299
00:23:27,190 --> 00:23:28,530
Is Bom Yi okay?

300
00:23:28,530 --> 00:23:29,880
Let me talk to her.

301
00:23:29,880 --> 00:23:31,340
Wait a moment.

302
00:23:31,340 --> 00:23:34,840
My wife wants to talk to Bom Yi.

303
00:23:37,480 --> 00:23:38,730
Hello?

304
00:23:38,730 --> 00:23:39,730
Bom Yi?

305
00:23:40,190 --> 00:23:41,430
