306
00:23:41,430 --> 00:23:42,470
Hello?

307
00:23:42,920 --> 00:23:44,150
<i>Mom.</i>

308
00:23:47,360 --> 00:23:48,690
Are you alright?

309
00:23:49,830 --> 00:23:51,120
Yes, mom.

310
00:23:52,710 --> 00:23:54,960
<i>There's a doctor here too...</i>

311
00:23:54,960 --> 00:23:58,430
<i>so don't worry, okay?</i>

312
00:24:00,360 --> 00:24:01,360
Okay.

313
00:24:04,360 --> 00:24:05,790
Give me the phone.

314
00:24:09,850 --> 00:24:11,010
Give me your hand.

315
00:24:14,500 --> 00:24:17,780
I want to call your mother too.

316
00:24:19,000 --> 00:24:19,850
Huh?

317
00:24:19,850 --> 00:24:22,060
I can't just call my parents.

318
00:24:22,060 --> 00:24:23,620
It's okay.

319
00:24:24,120 --> 00:24:26,640
She doesn't even know we're married.

320
00:24:26,640 --> 00:24:28,750
We didn't have a
proper wedding either.

321
00:24:28,750 --> 00:24:29,860
She'll be mad at me.

322
00:24:31,410 --> 00:24:34,470
I'll tell her about our wedding
when I get back...

323
00:24:34,470 --> 00:24:35,970
...but I still want to call her now.

324
00:24:47,460 --> 00:24:48,740
Hello?

325
00:24:49,350 --> 00:24:50,740
Hi, Miss Lee Bom Yi.

326
00:24:51,200 --> 00:24:54,580
Yes, it's me... mother.

327
00:24:58,270 --> 00:24:59,690
How are you?

328
00:25:00,210 --> 00:25:01,800
I'm fine.

329
00:25:02,610 --> 00:25:05,100
I'm sorry to worry you.

330
00:25:05,100 --> 00:25:07,350
