uncomfortable, isn't it?

333
00:25:12,470 --> 00:25:14,990
He's doing it because he likes it.

334
00:25:14,990 --> 00:25:18,270
Don't be sorry to me.
Use him as much as you need.

335
00:25:21,970 --> 00:25:25,560
I have to tell you something...

336
00:25:26,020 --> 00:25:27,390
...so I'll visit you soon.

337
00:25:27,390 --> 00:25:28,190
<i>No.</i>

338
00:25:28,190 --> 00:25:30,950
<i>You're sick.
You shouldn't come out.</i>

339
00:25:30,950 --> 00:25:32,470
Once you get better, call me...

340
00:25:32,470 --> 00:25:33,620
and I'll come visit you.

341
00:25:36,120 --> 00:25:37,690
Yes, I will.

342
00:25:39,300 --> 00:25:42,730
Being sick is just bad luck.

343
00:25:42,730 --> 00:25:45,870
Don't trouble your mind
with your sickness.

344
00:25:46,690 --> 00:25:50,240
<i>Your body will heal itself naturally
if your mind is healthy.</i>

345
00:25:50,450 --> 00:25:52,880
So just eat good food...

346
00:25:52,880 --> 00:25:54,880
and have good thoughts.

347
00:25:54,880 --> 00:25:56,210
<i>Okay?</i>

348
00:25:58,020 --> 00:25:59,920
Yes, thank you.

349
00:26:01,770 --> 00:26:03,880
Yes, I'll call you later.

350
00:26:09,410 --> 00:26:10,890
What did she tell you?

351
00:26:11,600 --> 00:26:13,560
She told me to use you
as much as I need.

352
00:26:14,830 --> 00:26:16,180
Of course.

353
00:26:17,260 --> 00:26:20,930
There's no one on my side
in my whole family.

354
00:26:25,720 --> 00:26:26,900
How do you feel?

355
00:26:27,470 --> 00:26:30,910
If you're up to it,
why don't we tour the island now?

356
00:26:33,430 --> 00:26:36,110
You told me that it takes
about five hours...

357
00:26:36,110 --> 00:26:38,150
...to walk around the island.

358
00:26:39,910 --> 00:26:41,660
I didn't say we'd walk.

359
00:27:16,090 --> 00:27:19,340
[Udo Lover]

360
00:27:34,810 --> 00:27:36,210
<i>If...</i>

361
00:27:37,290 --> 00:27:39,030
<i>...my heart...</i>

362
00:27:39,030 --> 00:27:42,760
<i>...sent me here...</i>

363
00:27:44,070 --> 00:27:46,860
<i>...I'd be much more
thankful than before.</i>

364
00:27:50,530 --> 00:27:53,550
<i>I don't love you
because of my heart...</i>

365
00:27:56,000 --> 00:27:59,070
<i>...but I do love you more because of it.</i>

366
00:28:14,460 --> 00:28:17,740
Can you see the windy hills over there?

367
00:28:21,770 --> 00:28:23,530
I can see them...

368
00:28:23,910 --> 00:28:26,300
...but they look even higher
than Halla Mountain to me.

369
00:28:28,500 --> 00:28:29,630
Don't you think so?

370
00:28:32,570 --> 00:28:34,800
Let's rest for today...

371
00:28:35,420 --> 00:28:38,440
and go there tomorrow
if you're up to it.

372
00:28:56,080 --> 00:28:57,530
I heard about Bom Yi.

373
00:28:58,030 --> 00:28:59,910
You must be very worried about her.

374
00:29:02,790 --> 00:29:03,890
Hyuk Soo.

375
00:29:03,890 --> 00:29:05,470
You surprised me.

376
00:29:05,470 --> 00:29:08,330
I didn't expect you to give up
the title of director so easily.

377
00:29:09,210 --> 00:29:10,970
It isn't a big deal to me.

378
00:29:11,700 --> 00:29:14,050
He isn't smart either.

379
00:29:14,580 --> 00:29:16,250
He refused a good offer to stay here.

380
00:29:17,070 --> 00:29:18,150
