be able to come here.

459
00:33:52,190 --> 00:33:55,220
By the way, whose helicopter was that?

460
00:33:55,880 --> 00:33:57,400
Was it Hyeong Woo's?

461
00:33:57,910 --> 00:33:59,330
It's mine.

462
00:34:00,000 --> 00:34:01,540
Ah, yes.

463
00:34:01,540 --> 00:34:03,230
Good for you.

464
00:34:04,290 --> 00:34:05,730
It was your first time, right?

465
00:34:05,730 --> 00:34:07,120
Weren't you scared?

466
00:34:07,120 --> 00:34:08,570
It wasn't my first time.

467
00:34:09,920 --> 00:34:11,870
I don't remember it well...

468
00:34:12,390 --> 00:34:13,730
but I rode in one...

469
00:34:15,040 --> 00:34:18,450
to get to the hospital on Jeju Island
for my operation.

470
00:34:24,680 --> 00:34:25,680
Speaking of...

471
00:34:26,460 --> 00:34:29,760
...didn't you say that your father
cut in line to get your heart?

472
00:34:30,500 --> 00:34:33,290
Yes, I believe so.

473
00:34:35,470 --> 00:34:37,520
My memory's a little fuzzy...

474
00:34:37,520 --> 00:34:41,400
about what I heard back then.

475
00:34:44,850 --> 00:34:46,390
I'm not sure...

476
00:34:47,410 --> 00:34:50,510
...but I think that he lied
about how critical my condition was.

477
00:34:54,490 --> 00:34:57,380
He was disciplined for it...

478
00:34:57,380 --> 00:35:00,190
and suspended as a surgeon.

479
00:35:01,280 --> 00:35:05,280
It ruined the hospital's reputation...

480
00:35:07,210 --> 00:35:09,370
so the hospital's been in trouble.

481
00:35:10,440 --> 00:35:13,140
That's why your father is...

482
00:35:14,660 --> 00:35:16,010
So free.

483
00:35:17,900 --> 00:35:21,610
I think that he thought it would only
cause problems temporarily.

484
00:35:38,420 --> 00:35:39,490
Hmm.

485
00:35:41,580 --> 00:35:44,930
What should we do now?

486
00:35:47,090 --> 00:35:48,420
Do you want to watch TV?

487
00:35:49,550 --> 00:35:50,980
I'd like to get some rest.

488
00:35:50,980 --> 00:35:51,980
Would you?

489
00:35:53,590 --> 00:35:56,360
I need to get enough rest
to go to the windy hills tomorrow.

490
00:35:56,860 --> 00:35:58,090
Yes, of course.

491
00:35:59,650 --> 00:36:00,950
Wait a minute.

492
00:36:02,510 --> 00:36:05,330
What was my friend
saying about the room?

493
00:36:52,730 --> 00:36:53,730
Wow...

494
00:37:21,190 --> 00:37:23,310
If you're sleeping beside me...

495
00:37:23,950 --> 00:37:27,260
...I wouldn't be scared
even if I hear the wind.

496
00:37:32,810 --> 00:37:35,340
Would you like me to
bring you some water?

497
00:37:36,410 --> 00:37:37,410
Yes.

498
00:38:29,770 --> 00:38:30,770
Bom Yi!

499
00:38:33,460 --> 00:38:34,440
Hey.

500
00:38:34,440 --> 00:38:35,450
Head up...

501
00:38:39,140 --> 00:38:41,070
It's okay.
It's okay.

502
00:38:53,820 --> 00:38:54,820
Bom Yi.

503
00:38:59,780 --> 00:39:01,260
Come on, I'm here.

504
00:39:01,260 --> 00:39:02,750
Don't be scared.

505
00:39:02,750 --> 00:39:03,770
Slowly...

506
00:39:04,040 --> 00:39:06,010
Breathe slowly.

507
00:39:06,010 --> 00:39:07,170
Slowly...

508
00:39:08,240 --> 00:39:09,610
Slowly...

509
00:39:10,710 --> 00:39:11,760
That's right.

510
00:39:15,070 --> 00:39:16,110
How are you?

511
00:39:17,140 --> 00:39:18,550
You're okay, right?

512
00:39:34,560 --> 00:39:36,470
You have such a nice husband.

513
00:39:36,610 --> 00:39:39,320
He took very good care of you.

514
00:39:39,320 --> 00:39:42,770
You should go back to Seoul
in the morning.

515
00:39:43,230 --> 00:39:45,290
You can't take care
of her properly here.

516
00:39:45,290 --> 00:39:47,400
What I did is only
a temporary expedient, so...

517
00:39:49,070 --> 00:39:50,780
What about the windy hills?

518
00:39:51,460 --> 00:39:52,660
No way.

519
00:39:52,660 --> 00:39:54,170
Don't even think about it.

520
00:39:54,700 --> 00:39:55,700
Okay?

521
00:39:56,610 --> 00:39:57,700
Okay?

522
00:39:58,240 --> 00:39:59,360
Thank you.

523
00:40:11,700 --> 00:40:12,950
I'm sorry...

524
00:40:12,950 --> 00:40:14,320
for surprising you.

525
00:40:15,500 --> 00:40:17,080
I wasn't surprised at all.

526
00:40:22,380 --> 00:40:25,760
I don't think that we can go.

527
00:40:26,410 --> 00:40:27,410
Right?

528
00:40:36,740 --> 00:40:38,940
Can I get some fresh air?

529
00:40:39,770 --> 00:40:41,400
It's stuffy in here.

530
00:40:52,010 --> 00:40:54,690
Thank you for bringing me here.

531
00:40:56,540 --> 00:40:59,030
If you want anything...

532
00:40:59,030 --> 00:41:00,710
...tell me anytime.

533
00:41:03,590 --> 00:41:04,590
I'm sorry.

534
00:41:07,340 --> 00:41:09,500
Why do you keep apologizing?

535
00:41:10,280 --> 00:41:12,390
I'm so happy right now.

536
00:41:14,540 --> 00:41:16,170
Maybe...

537
00:41:17,780 --> 00:41:20,700
we weren't allowed
to love each other...

538
00:41:22,550 --> 00:41:25,410
...which is why we pushed
each other away...

539
00:41:26,320 --> 00:41:28,470
and we tried to leave each other.

540
00:41:30,680 --> 00:41:32,810
But now we're here...

541
00:41:33,590 --> 00:41:35,390
as a married couple.

542
00:41:43,600 --> 00:41:47,600
At first we sat here...

543
00:41:49,060 --> 00:41:51,060
and talked about old stories.

544
00:41:53,140 --> 00:41:56,210
Then we sat here...

545
00:41:57,760 --> 00:41:59,940
and talked about the future...

546
00:42:01,060 --> 00:42:02,720
so for now...

547
00:42:04,340 --> 00:42:06,120
let's just talk about the present.

548
00:42:06,930 --> 00:42:08,080
What if...

549
00:42:09,250 --> 00:42:10,700
...by some chance...

550
00:42:12,820 --> 00:42:15,160
...I don't wake up tomorrow?

551
00:42:24,540 --> 00:42:27,790
That won't happen.

